snippet: France will stick to its timetable for withdrawing troops from Mali despite a resurgence in violence and the killing of two French journalists last weekend, Foreign Minister Laurent Fabius said Tuesday.
lead_paragraph: France will stick to its timetable for withdrawing troops from Mali despite a resurgence in violence and the killing of two French journalists last weekend, Foreign Minister Laurent Fabius said Tuesday.

headline.main: Mali: France Says It Will Not Delay Troop Withdrawal
headline.print_headline: Mali: France Says It Will Not Delay Troop Withdrawal
